This package acts as a to do list where the user can enter a set a tasks for the day and it will send a text file containing the list
of their tasks for the day. It can be run as a concurrent program in Oracle and set to run every day.

Example...

============================================================================================
Date: FEB 28, 2020
Tasks to finish today: 3
Tasks Completed: 0
Tasks Pending: 3
============================================================================================
                                                                                            
Remaining Tasks...
                                                                                            
1: Task 1 description
2: Task 2 description
3: Task 3 description
etc

--Displays table information where the tasks are stored
Column Name    ID    Null?  Data Type                 Default
TASK	         1			N	    NUMBER		  								
TASK_ID	       2			N	    VARCHAR2    (5 Byte)										
PRIORITY	     3			N	    VARCHAR2    (15 Byte)										
DESCRIPTION	   4			Y   	VARCHAR2    (100 Byte)	  'N/A'									
APPROX_TIME	   5			Y   	VARCHAR2    (55 Byte)	    'N/A'									
STATUS	       6			Y   	VARCHAR2    (15 Byte)	    'PENDING'									
